high_descs: Turn around and go near the microwave.
Take the peach from the microwave oven.
Turn around and go to the sidetable.
Put the peach on the sidetable.
Turn around and go near to the toilet.
Take the another peach from the toilet sink.
Turn around and go to the sidetable.
Put the peach on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Collect the Peach and placed it on the SideTable.

high_descs: Head into the kitchen area on the left and go to the microwave.
Remove the peach from the microwave.
Head through the door on the left of the kitchen area, entering the bedroom, heading to the back of the sidetable.
Place the peach on the sidetable behind the bed.
Exit the room the way you came in, walk ahead to the fridge, then follow the wall along the right of the fridge to enter the toilet.
Pick up the peach from the top of the toilet tank.
Return to the sidetable behind the bed where you placed the first apple.
Place the second peach down next to the first one on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two peach on long stands behind a SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around to reach the kitchen on the right and head to the microwave.
Take out the peach from the microwave.
Turn around and head to the bedroom on the right to reach the sidetable behind the bed.
Put the peach on the sidetable.
Turn around and walk out the bedroom and turn right to reach the sink on the left to reach the toilet.
Pick up the peach from the toilet.
Turn around to exit the room and turn right to reach the bedroom on the right and face the sidetable behind the bed.
Put the peach on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put two peachs on the SideTable.
